Detailed Description

CMSIS Cortex-M0+ Device Peripheral Access Layer Header File. This file contains all the peripheral register's definitions, bits definitions and memory mapping for stm32l073xx devices.

Author
MCD Application Team This file contains:
  • Data structures and the address mapping for all peripherals
  • Peripheral's registers declarations and bits definition
  • Macros to access peripheral's registers hardware
